s, it was…","fields":{"date":"2021-06-03T06:28:35.614Z","slug":"/blog/my-first-month-as-a-freelancer/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Quitting, Moving, & Getting Bit By A Dog","subtitle":"My First Month As A Freelancer","tags":["Freelance","Career"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/6b695/featuredImage.png","srcSet":"/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/2141d/featuredImage.png 132w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/7d3c7/featuredImage.png 263w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/6b695/featuredImage.png 526w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/c683a/featuredImage.png 1052w","sizes":"(min-width: 526px) 526px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/87113/featuredImage.webp 132w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/90103/featuredImage.webp 263w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/328c9/featuredImage.webp 526w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/30766/featuredImage.webp 1052w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 526px) 526px, 100vw"}]},"width":526,"height":350}}}}},{"id":"f861f4a3-3850-55ae-81d1-b2d67aa4088d","excerpt":"Shopify is the most customizable e-commerce platform, while still being super user friendly out of the box. Like yes, hypothetically you can…","fields":{"date":"2022-01-08T02:35:50.953Z","slug":"/blog/organize-your-shopify-settings/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Organize Your Shopify Theme & Section Settings","subtitle":"","tags":["Shopify","E-Commerce"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#98b848","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/254bc/featuredImage.png","srcSet":"/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/c2a4a/featuredImage.png 167w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/fe850/featuredImage.png 334w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/254bc/featuredImage.png 667w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/6f72c/featuredImage.png 1334w","sizes":"(min-width: 667px) 667px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/bcba2/featuredImage.webp 167w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/fb036/featuredImage.webp 334w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/bbe13/featuredImage.webp 667w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/994d2/featuredImage.webp 1334w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 667px) 667px, 100vw"}]},"width":667,"height":350}}}}}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}